                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p><strong>Requirements</strong> The retail employee has a creature's credstick</p><hr /><p><strong>Effect</strong> The employee transfers 1d100 credits to their own credstick, charging the creature for their services. The creature must succeed at a @Check[will|dc:15] save or become @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.conditions.Item.Fascinated] with retrieving their credstick for 1 round (2 rounds on a critical failure). If the creature does not have sufficient credits, the employee has a +2 circumstance bonus to Strikes against the creature for 1 minute.</p>"
